				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I haven't checked all spells, but a few I have, now that the pet buff timer is there.
<br />

<br />
I two box a shaman all the time (when my brother isn't playing him, as it's his charcter), and he has extended buffs. Alot of buffs I've noticed, but the main one I've noticed (that matters the most to me) is FA. Ferine Avatar is a huge dmg bonus to pet, but on pet it will only last the regular time of the buff, which is 6 and a half minutes or so. If i cast it on my character it lasts 10 minutes. Has anyone else noticed problems with extended enhancement not working on pets?</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
			</tr>
