				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">My opinion is that the difference is sometimes a bug, and sometimes due to lag.  
<br />

<br />
There are times that kei fades immediately after I zone, even though I just got it.  That is a bug.  
<br />

<br />
I also think lag varies depending on where you are in a zone.  Sometimes one char is far away from the rest of our boxed group, and when the others ld the further-away char doesn't--all char are on a single router, and the LD members all are disconnected at the same time.  
<br />

<br />
So therefore if the pet is further away it is subject to a variation in lag compared with the magician, as when you are traveling.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
